<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>상품 수정 | Seoyeon Tour</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif; background: #f4f5f7; }
        .sidebar {
            width: 240px;
            height: 100vh;
            background: #1a1a2e;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0; left: 0;
            padding: 32px 20px;
            color: #fff;
        }
        .sidebar .brand {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .sidebar .nav-link {
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6) !important;
            font-size: 0.88rem;
            padding: 10px 12px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .sidebar .nav-link:hover {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            color: #fff !important;
        }
        .main-content { margin-left: 240px; padding: 40px; }
        .edit-card {
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 36px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
            max-width: 800px;
        }
        .section-title {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1a1a2e;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            padding-bottom: 12px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        .form-label { font-size: 0.82rem; color: #666; font-weight: 500; }
        .form-control, .form-select { font-size: 0.85rem; }
        .current-img {
            width: 120px;
            height: 80px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="sidebar">
        <div class="brand">SEOYEON ADMIN</div>
        <nav class="nav flex-column">
            <a class="nav-link" href="/admin#products">상품 관리</a>
            <a class="nav-link" href="/admin#events">이벤트 관리</a>
            <a class="nav-link" href="/admin#users">회원 관리</a>
            <a class="nav-link" href="/admin#payments">결제 관리</a>
            <hr style="border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); margin: 20px 0;">
            <a class="nav-link" href="/">홈으로</a>
            <a class="nav-link" href="/auth/logout" style="color: rgba(255,100,100,0.8) !important;">로그아웃</a>
        </nav>
    </div>

    <div class="main-content">
        <div class="edit-card">
            <div class="section-title">상품 수정</div>

            <form action="/admin/product/edit" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
                <input type="hidden" name="product_id" value="<%= product.product_id %>">
                <input type="hidden" name="current_image" value="<%= product.image %>">

                <div class="row g-3 mb-4">
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <label class="form-label">카테고리</label>
                        <select name="category" class="form-select" required>
                            <option value="honeymoon-europe" <%= product.category === 'honeymoon-europe' ? 'selected' : '' %>>허니문-유럽</option>
                            <option value="honeymoon-resort" <%= product.category === 'honeymoon-resort' ? 'selected' : '' %>>허니문-휴양지</option>
                            <option value="group" <%= product.category === 'group' ? 'selected' : '' %>>단체여행</option>
                            <option value="package" <%= product.category === 'package' ? 'selected' : '' %>>패키지</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <label class="form-label">상품명</label>
                        <input type="text" name="product_name" class="form-control" value="<%= product.product_name %>" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <label class="form-label">가격</label>
                        <input type="number" name="price" class="form-control" value="<%= product.price %>" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <label class="form-label">여행지</label>
                        <input type="text" name="destination" class="form-control" value="<%= product.destination %>">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <label class="form-label">기간</label>
                        <input type="text" name="duration" class="form-control" value="<%= product.duration %>">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-12">
                        <label class="form-label">이미지</label>
                        <div>
                            <img src="/images/<%= product.image %>" class="current-img" alt="현재 이미지">
                            <p class="text-muted small">현재: <%= product.image %></p>
                        </div>
                        <input type="file" name="image" class="form-control" accept="image/*">
                        <p class="text-muted small mt-1">새 이미지를 선택하지 않으면 기존 이미지가 유지됩니다.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <hr class="my-4">
                <p class="fw-bold mb-3" style="font-size:0.9rem;">상세 정보</p>

                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label class="form-label">소개 (description)</label>
                    <textarea name="description" class="form-control" rows="2"><%= product.description || '' %></textarea>
                </div>
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label class="form-label">주요 명소 (highlights)</label>
                    <textarea name="highlights" class="form-control" rows="2"><%= product.highlights || '' %></textarea>
                </div>
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label class="form-label">포함 사항 (included)</label>
                    <textarea name="included" class="form-control" rows="2"><%= product.included || '' %></textarea>
                </div>
                <div class="mb-4">
                    <label class="form-label">여행 일정 (schedule)</label>
                    <p class="text-muted small">줄바꿈으로 구분. 예: 1일차: 인천 출발<br>2일차: 관광</p>
                    <textarea name="schedule" class="form-control" rows="6"><%= product.schedule || '' %></textarea>
                </div>

                <div class="d-flex gap-2">
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-dark px-4">저장</button>
                    <a href="/admin" class="btn btn-outline-secondary px-4">취소</a>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
